    def bias_init_with_prob(prior_prob = 0.01)

Initialize conv/fc bias value according to a given probability value.

This function calculates the bias initialization value based on a prior probability using the inverse sigmoid (logit) function. It's commonly used in object detection models to initialize classification layers with a specific positive prediction probability.

